TreeNode.Name: GPS Tracking system that improves work-flow
Benefits of using Softex GPS Tracker
TreeNode.Description:
A non-complexed system that allow the user (Employee) to share his GPS Check-ins or live location with manager (Employer) for business purposes. The user can share and write comments about his current location stamped with date and time to be shared only with his corporate account manager.
 
Nevertheless.. Get subscribed to enjoy the Live tracking feature that allow an instant monitoring for your team performance.
 
“Managing resources will empower your business insight“
Softex GPS Tracking system help companies get a grip on labor costs, especially overtime, and those who own large sales force and technical support teams or maintenance crew, since it is functional for keeping the track of their employees. Otherwise, it will help managers to make a solid evaluation based on the efficient system reports.
  
Softex GPS Benefits
Ready to automate your operations with GPS smart tracker?
Manage employee’s records, data, and locations in one secure place that is scalable and easy to access from anywhere.

TreeNode.Name: How it works?
TreeNode.Description:
Web-based Admin Panel
Fleet management system designed to boost employee’s wellbeing, through a user-friendly interface admin will be able to create, manage, and report employee’s check-ins and outs with remarks.
 
 Mobile Application for employees          
 
Trustworthy and accuracy and to make employees experience world-class, this is the main factors to start using Softex GPS Tracking mobile application.
 
To let users, feel comfortable that their efforts are not wasted, by locating and reporting to their leaders with a detailed summary from both sides, Softex GPS Tracker generate accurate location data whatever the end-user (Employee) is connected to the internet or not, and once connected again all the data shall be sent to the admin panel.
